<!-- ════════════════ FAQ ════════════════ -->
<section class="landing-feature landing-feature-alt" id="faq">
    <div class="landing-container">
        <div class="landing-section-header">
            <span class="landing-section-tag">FAQ</span>
            <h2>Frequently asked<br><strong>questions.</strong></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="landing-faq-list">
            <details class="landing-faq-item">
                <summary>What is Fund-Raise?</summary>
                <p>Fund-Raise is a fundraising intelligence platform built for foundations and nonprofits. It combines real-time dashboards, AI-powered analytics, and writing tools to help fundraising teams track performance, understand donor behavior, and work more efficiently.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="landing-faq-item">
                <summary>How does the AI assistant work?</summary>
                <p>Ask Fund-Raise uses advanced AI (Claude by Anthropic) to answer natural-language questions about your fundraising data. It can look up donors in your Blackbaud CRM, analyze trends, compare campaigns, and generate insights — all through a simple chat interface.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="landing-faq-item">
                <summary>Is my data secure?</summary>
                <p>Yes. All data is encrypted in transit (TLS) and at rest. Authentication is handled through Google OAuth 2.0, and we use role-based access control to ensure users only see data appropriate to their role. We never sell or share your data with third parties.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="landing-faq-item">
                <summary>Do I need Blackbaud RE NXT?</summary>
                <p>No. Blackbaud integration is optional. Fund-Raise works as a standalone platform using uploaded spreadsheet data. The Blackbaud integration adds real-time CRM lookups for organizations that use Raiser's Edge NXT.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="landing-faq-item">
                <summary>How do I upload our data?</summary>
                <p>Authorized users can drag and drop department Excel spreadsheets directly into Fund-Raise. The system automatically processes the data, creates historical snapshots, and updates all dashboards and metrics.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="landing-faq-item">
                <summary>Is Fund-Raise free?</summary>
                <p>Fund-Raise is currently available at no cost for qualifying foundations and nonprofit organizations. Contact us to learn about access and eligibility.</p>
            </details>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

